        "jsCode": "let msg = $json[\"message\"][\"content\"];\n\n// Convertir markdown básico a HTML\nmsg = msg\n  .replace(/\\*\\*(.*?)\\*\\*/g, '<strong>$1</strong>')  // negrita\n  .replace(/\\*(.*?)\\*/g, '<em>$1</em>')               // cursiva\n  .replace(/\\n/g, '<br>');                            // saltos de línea\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    message: msg\n  }\n};\n"
